{"tid":1660051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登既熱門計算方法令咁多標題黨既post出現","createTime":"2019-10-17T09:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T09:43:34.000Z","uid":61886,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fc524ffbe6e05010f2e5a7753ec2301ec7e3a0d0","tid":1660051,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:35:31.000Z","msg":"連登post點計熱門?<br />\n<br />\n係計有幾多人入去個post度<br />\n唔係計留言 唔係計正負評<br />\n所以點解咁多人個標題都寫到曄眾取寵<br />\n就係引人入去<br />\n然後就上熱門<br />\n令一d正經topic既post沉晒底<br />\n<br />\n個人建議連登修改熱門post計法，建議有二:<br />\n1. 增設熱門評分，由各用戶評分是否應上熱門，高分post+一定既評分就上熱門，太低分就拉返走。<br />\n2. 按留言用戶人數決定上唔上熱門，只要大家廢post唔留言就ok。(用戶人數決定，而非留言量，避免小圈子推post)<br />\n<br />\n請連仔幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都推post推到傻<br />\n寫正經野都要開個誇撚張既topic先有人理<br />\n<br />\nbtw<br />\n請幫推此戰術post<br />\n<br />\n而家前線係非常危險 因為警犬已經轉左策略<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/akojcFU\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/akojcFU</a>"},{"pid":"98ced41cf8829a2cff6db2523b542ead09908684","tid":1660051,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:35:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afoWPNY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafoWPNY.jpg&h=041452ea&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"89973bddd8cd0874f3e270d10d120c48cb48f6c3","tid":1660051,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:36:37.000Z","msg":"個post個topic唔夠爆<br />\n應該有排推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed49ec4c89f7fd7591dcb2d6bd0f0a921d62f28f","tid":1660051,"uid":102535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T09:36:40.000Z","msg":"我都開post講過<br />\n幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全部同我入嚟支持民記</span></strong> <br />\n<code>[第二十次民間記者會]</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1659956\" dat